<item>
            <title>[CXF-3719] NullPointerException When using TransformOutInterceptor</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3719</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have attempted to remove the namespace prefixes outbound JSON messages by using the TransformOutInterceptor.  At line 87 it explicitly does&lt;br/&gt;
    message.removeContent(OutputStream.class);&lt;br/&gt;
and this eventually causes a NullPointerException in the constructor of java.io.Writer.  The MessageImpl class has an array called defaultContents that would have otherwise had an entry containing HTTPConduit$WrappedOutputStream that would have been passed through multiple layer to the constructor of java.io.writer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Linux 2.6.29, java 1.6.0_16&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12518232">CXF-3719</key>
